This method is unused now, remove?

Also, if you need this in the future, the most straightforward and efficient implementation is:

```
int64_t getArgumentIndex(mlir::FuncOp op, Value value) {
  BlockArgument arg = dyn_cast<BlockArgument>(value);
  if (!arg || arg.getOwner() != &op.front()) return -1;
  return arg.getArgNumber();
}
```
